LOCAL SETUP (WSL + PHP)

1) Copy env template and adjust credentials if needed:
   cp .env.example .env

2) Create database and load schema:
   mysql -h 127.0.0.1 -P 3306 -u root -p < sql/schema.sql

3) Start local PHP server from project root:
   php -S 127.0.0.1:8000 -t public

4) Open in browser:
   http://127.0.0.1:8000

5) Optional DB diagnostics (CLI):
   php test_db_connection.php

